	  SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-26-13): bug	1177,1216: It seems that eval() is
	  the correct format we should be using. NOT eval {}. I believe the
	  correct fix to the "eval problem", in its various manifestations
	  in bug 1168, bug 1073, bug 987, bug 1216 is that we should use
	  eval(), as we used to do originally, but "unshift" the Bugzilla
	  path, instead of "push" it. This would guarantee that the
	  Bugzilla library is added first. This was described in bug 1168,
	  comment 17.

