	  SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-26-8, SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-26-7,
	  SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-26-6): bug 1118: Merged most of the changes from
	  attachment 346 which was a patch by Robert Hudson
	  <rhudson@tibco.com> that extends the existing WebReports. This
	  includes:

	  - Ability to flag bugs with if they have been code reviewed
	  (codestriker interaction) and if the review has been completed or
	  is still open. [This is a very useful feature if you have a
	  policy that any "patch" releases to customers should have
	  everything code reviewed before release]

	  - A set of new example pages that extend the existing
	  functionality so that you can have an entire release process.
	  The first additional page prompts the user with a generic form to
	  complete to gather release information.  The second additional
	  page then takes that input information and generates an html view
	  of the information with additions summaries of each bug.

