	  (1.34, SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-14-1): bug 711: Introduced a new autoconf
	  variable that will hold the comment token for the OS the codebase
	  was configured in a format that can be used in a regular
	  expression. For example the '#' token for UNIX is used as '\#' in
	  a regular expression. It must be escaped or else the entire
	  expression is considered a comment and is ignored.

