	  SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-8-3): SCMBUG ID:   441 SCMBUG NOTE: Modified the
	  mechanism in which the log template is provided to permit the
	  user to define in the glue configuration file two regular
	  expressions for detecting the list of bug ids and the log
	  comment. The result is that one is no longer restricted to having
	  to type each time the 2 tokens for detecting the bug id (SCMBUG
	  ID:) and log comment (SCMBUG NOTE:), which was rather annoying
	  especially in the case of Subversion that does not even supply a
	  default template.

