	  p_kpm_paper_introduce_draft1, p_kpm_paper_introduce_draft2,
	  SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-3-1, SCMBUG_RELEASE_0-3-0),
	  lib/product/Daemon.pm.in (1.12), lib/product/Glue.pm.in (1.10):
	  SCMBUG ID:  421 SCMBUG NOTE: Added the capability of specifying a
	  list of product names. When that happens, tagging activities will
	  not be issued to the integration daemon, since tha daemon cannot
	  determine which product name the tagging corresponds to. During
	  bug id verification checks, it is verified whether the list of
	  bug ids belong to any of the products specified in the glue
	  configuration file.

