2004-08-10 Tuesday 08:14  mkgnu

	* src/lib/product/Bugzilla.pm.in (1.8): SCMBUG ID:  396 SCMBUG
	  NOTE:Reverted back to removing the data/versioncache file rather
	  than calling GenerateVersionTable(). The reason is:

	  # ls -lrtah data/versioncache -rw-rw----    1 apache	 apache
	     16K Aug 10 01:05 data/versioncache

	  When the Scmbug daemon runs as root, it is not able to recreate
	  this file using GenerateVersionTable(). It's unclear why, but
	  that's what happens.

